name: A Val3ntin3 by thr33som3s - Pink Insert - FOR LOV3RS ONLY - #3V001
description:
You’ve received a Val3ntin3!!! 

But, this isn’t just any old val3ntin3.   This one is directly from thr33som3s, and it’s a special thank you for all you did during the First Pink Insert Drop.

Val3ntin3s are a special type of thr33som3s Insert which was made to be given away. — those who received this as an airdrop went ABOVE AND BEYOND… they are collectors who spent their own money to give away over FORTY-FIVE THOUSAND Val3ntin3s.
